

----------------------Docker pull request = "docker pull sefalett/hamspammodelro:latest" --------------------------------
---------------------- To run image = "docker run --publish 5000:5000 sefalett/hamspammodelpro:latest -------------------




*********************************************************** Dockerfile Build Method ***********************************************************

************ FOR WINDOWS POWERSHELL ************
 
 To acces your file path = "cd "Your file path""
 
 To build the Dockerfile = "docker build --tag ham_spam ."
 
 To run the container = "docker run -d -p 5000:5000 ham_spam"
 
 ************ FOR BROWSER SEARCH BAR ************
 
 To access the app = "127.0.0.1:5000"
